OL,4,Cdad found dead together
OL,6,FAn independent review will take place
OL,7,Finto the deaths of a two-year-old boy
OL,8,Fand his father in .
OL,10,FIt is believed Bronson Battersby died
OL,11,Ffrom starvation days after his father,
OL,12,FKenneth, had a fatal heart attack.
OL,14,FTheir bodies were found next to each
OL,15,Fother at a flat in the town on 9
OL,16,FJanuary, two weeks after they were
OL,17,Flast seen.
OL,19,FAfter a "rapid review", social
OL,20,Fservices have now commissioned a more-
OL,21,Fin depth investigation.
