OL,6,FIt will involve safeguarding officials
OL,7,Ffrom Lincolnshire County Council,
OL,8,FLincolnshire PoliceJand health sector
OL,9,Forganisations and look at how similar
OL,10,Fincidents could be prevented.
OL,12,FThe review is expected to take six
OL,13,Fmonths.
