OL,6,FChris Cook, independent chair of the
OL,7,FLincolnshire Safeguarding Children
OL,8,FPartnership, said: "Keeping children
OL,9,Fsafe is a priority for all local
OL,10,Fagencies, and it's important we take
OL,11,Ftime to explore fully the
OL,12,Fcircumstances surrounding this tragic
OL,13,Fincident and identify any potential
OL,14,Fimprovements we could make.
OL,16,F"To that end, we will be commissioning
OL,17,Fan independent author to make a
OL,18,Fdetailed analysis of the work of local
OL,19,Fsafeguarding partners.
